  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators performed a 12-week, randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled human
      trial to evaluate the efficacy and safety of Fermented Cinnamon Vine Powde on decrement of
      body fat. The investigators measured decrement of body fat parameters , including abdominal
      fat, Body Fat Mass, LDL-C, HDL-C, Total Cholesterol and triglyceride, and monitored their
      blood pressure.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
